parameters:
【Skeleton Head】 Phew... I want to grab Carbuncle's
butt like an eagle.
【Masamune】 This person...

【Tommy】 Hey, wanna take a break? I'm feeling
tired.
【Masamune】 Yeah, let's take a break for a bit.
【Tommy】 Phew...

【Tommy】 It seems bigger than I thought. I never
expected there to be a place like this in the
chapel.

【Leon】 Tommy is knowledgeable about secret
passages and hidden rooms.
【Masamune】 Is that so? That's amazing.

【Tommy】 I just read a lot of books in the Great
Library. Sometimes there are things written in the
magic books left behind by previous graduates.

【Tommy】 The magical spaces in the academy are
mostly created by former students during their
time here.
【Masamune】 Oh, really?

【Tommy】 And so, that's where most of the treasures
are hidden.
【Leon】 That's interesting, isn't it?

【Tommy】 The remaining spaces are often left
untouched because the people who created them
never returned.

【Tommy】 That's why the luggage and everything are
left as they are.
【Masamune】 I wonder why they didn't come back.
【Leon】 Obviously, they were killed by monsters.
【Masamune】 Ah...
【Masamune】 So, this place too...
【Tommy】 There is a possibility, isn't there?

【Masamune】 If that's the case, it seems a bit like
grave robbing.
【Tommy】 Certainly...

【Leon】 Don't worry about it. Even if we don't
investigate, it will just continue to be
abandoned.

【Masamune】 But, let's offer our prayers just in
case.
A
【Masamune】It's clean water.

【Tommy】 This is holy water. I wonder if the sister
has blessed it.

【Masamune】 I'm saved. Now I just need something to
scoop this water with.
【Masamune】Use this jar to fetch water...
